Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与魔术师{\c&H00FFFF60}的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然睡了一会儿  但是好像早晨还没有到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这里是没有太阳的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.43,0:02:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边能看见遮阳的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小狼  真聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都行  快把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  雪兔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊先生  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吓到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个国家居住的人们都能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为擅长生成衣服的魔法而开了裁缝店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擅长制成食物的魔法  就开了这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？前任国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么恭敬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  不要再说那个没用的称号了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不可以的  这是事实嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家是从平民当中评选国王的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃矢以前做过国王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪是「前任国王陛下」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家里的人民每年会做同样的一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦里出现的人就会成为下一任国王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今年选出的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然住在城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道为什么  不去做国王该履行的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为国王的失职  引起了很大的灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家再也没有迎来过白天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明之夜已经持续了好几个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的魔力的源泉来自于太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  因为夜晚一直持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得不到太阳的恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力开始退化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这种状况持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的结果将难以想象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再考虑那么多伤脑筋的事也没用的  来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在樱都国曾经见到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的可比现在要大得多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在罗嗦些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带领大家去城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到国王的城堡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接舞蹈马上就要上演了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是服侍国王的魔法精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么带我们来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情想和你谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？和我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是魔法师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想请你使用你的魔法  去了解国王的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说服她登上王位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？但是这个国家里会使用魔法的\N除了我还有很多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都试过了  结果全失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想再请身为旅人的你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用你的魔法拯救这个国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这可受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想帮助你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我已经决定不再使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带大家去特别客房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么特别客房！明明是监狱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢像猛兽一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  黑钢好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿  这个国家有没有公主的羽毛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？小摩可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有羽毛的话  就不用一直待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有奇怪的家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去挡住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个先逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  拜拜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为只有这个方法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你要怎么办  法伊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  亲手封印了阿修罗王之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能再待在这个国家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该是这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到没有阿修罗王的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是今年被选出来的国王继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想和她说话是白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的记忆全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为国王的人  必须有纯净的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  在登上王位之前  把她之前的记忆全都被消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在换国王的时候  她的记忆会全都恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子  看上去好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎  那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有记忆  所以也不会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿没有说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子的寂寞是因为不能出城造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实她是非常非常想出去到处玩玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却不行  所以很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧大人要是回不了城堡的话就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝茉茉担心的好想跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们分头找  一定要把他们找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多烦人的东西聚集着  想出也出不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊他们到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有可能在那个店里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  可是没有别的可以拜托的人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  之后你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和唧一起玩  直到她尽兴为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很热的  要当心别烫到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微记住几句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  复习一下说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…唧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊  再教我多一点词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊是从哪里来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很远很远的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道是哪里呢  我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我绝对不要回到以前的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧  不怎么明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在逃避呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  为了逃避与某个人的再次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊好像很寂寞的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哦  看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.90,0:15:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和法伊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很感谢…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该道谢的好像该是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没有过这种心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被做出来的生命？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对魔法极为精通的人开放的究极之术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是创造生命的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次被选出的唧国王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由这个国家里拥有最高能力的伟大魔法师制造出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像唧那样的人  虽然数量不是很多  但是还有几个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也能使用魔法  外表看上去和我们没有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔法创造出来的生命  不能从这个城里离开一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造生命的魔法只在这个城里面有效力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如即使只是从城里迈出去一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧的身体也会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊知道这件事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然告诉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承国王的唧如果发生了假设的那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明之夜将永远继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要避免那种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小狼  黑磷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里说感谢的话了  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门似乎被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧大人出去了就糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑钢先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也没法分身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去啊  唧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出了这扇门  你就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊  和唧一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧想一直一直和法伊一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧想和法伊一起…一直一直…逃避！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避是很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的话  痛苦也会减半的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为如果是两个人  悲伤也可能加倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊所说的这些  不想去明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回去吧  大家都在等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明之夜的天也终于破晓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唧大人回来这里了  可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你  法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我  是唧自己决定的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  谢谢你  唧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是分别的问候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以后还会再会的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  法伊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:22:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.56,0:24:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿不小心犯了大错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎把法伊和黑碰丢到什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向受困的小狼和小樱伸出援助之手的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.75,0:24:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超帅的叫做铃兰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.66,0:24:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  小狼  那身打扮是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.17,0:24:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道小狼到底是什么打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.81,0:24:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请继续期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.51,0:24:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.00,0:24:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修罗的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.40,0:24:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回会为小樱的危机而期待不已
